<item>
            <title>[LU-14190] remove DES3 enctype support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14190</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The krb5 releases 1.18 and later completely remove support for all DES3 enctypes (des3-cbc-raw, des3-hmac-sha1, des3-cbc-sha1-kd).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
